Package: corihw
Type: Package
Title: Independent Hypothesis Weighting for Correlated Tests
Version: 0.1.0
Authoers@R: (person("Yair", "Goldberg", email = "yair.goldy@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")
Author: Yair Goldberg [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yair Goldberg <yair.goldy@gmail.com>
Description: This package generalizes independent hypothesis weighting (IHW)  multiple testing
    procedure to correlated tests. It enavle to use covarites that are informative
    under the alternative to increases power when the tests are correlated.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyData: true
Imports: methods, tidyverse, dplyr, tibble, Matrix, nloptr, IHW, slam, rARPACK,lpsymphony, fdrtool
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
